1.title: Brazil
1.plot: A Rare And Fascinating Look Inside The World's Most Grueling Military Competition: Fuerzas Comando. The competition was held in Colombia and included troops from the United States, and 20 Western Hemisphere nations. The documentary focuses on the intensity of the annual competition, the unique Special Forces skill sets, and the tight-knit camaraderie between the region's brotherhood of elite warriors.
